The,OpenStack,Database,is,a,scalable,cloud,based,service,for,managing,database,engines,This,service,works,with,the,OpenStack,Database,API,to,simplify,and,expedite,the,deployment,of,database,features,and,functionalities,The,API,makes,it,easier,for,developers,to,facilitate,the,simultaneous,accessibility,and,exploitation,multiple,database,instances,The,API,mainly,conveys,HTTP,formatted,requests,and,responses